divs: Sighting DetailsOur uncle was taking a pic of the beautiful sunset in front of him, when a big bright object suddenly brightened the sky while he was taking the picture. H was saving it and when he looked back it was already gone. Her said he was felt a little fear (he was in the middle of the Arizona desert.) He also told me that he's seen other things before, but never like this and captured in a picture.
